Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.98,0:00:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,3004)}So Ra No Wo To
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.52,0:01:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have you practice with only\Nthe mouthpiece for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.49,0:01:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.67,0:01:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! But, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.72,0:02:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be able to play songs like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.78,0:02:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't make it easy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ready for anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's breakfast time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.96,0:02:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mess hall is over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.23,0:02:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.63,0:02:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rough and ragged.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.01,0:02:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.95,0:02:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First Battle -\NA Chair Story
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, we prepared it to\Nwelcome you last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.17,0:03:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A little treat for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.51,0:03:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.33,0:03:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you bring in the fish\NI was drying upstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.08,0:03:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.39,0:03:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Noël.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.53,0:03:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can sleep after breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.00,0:03:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not doing your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.86,0:03:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing my best...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.65,0:03:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Rio-sempai's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:03:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.98,0:04:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Breakfast will get cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.57,0:04:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me reintroduce you to\Neveryone in the 1121 Platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.79,0:04:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.81,0:04:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Filicia Heidemann.\NI'm a tank commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.47,0:04:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have fun while you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.65,0:04:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.51,0:04:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.59,0:04:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Noël.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.68,0:04:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël Kannagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Corporal Kannagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's our mechanic, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.45,0:04:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Private Kureha Suminoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the gunner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.88,0:05:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm younger than you, but I've been here\Nlonger, so you'd better do as I-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.27,0:05:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.04,0:05:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything, Noël-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.91,0:05:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, let's get to breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Then let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.96,0:05:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.06,0:05:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cut the bacon myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.53,0:05:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soldiers and trumpeters\Nboth need stamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.38,0:06:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat a lot and grow strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.99,0:06:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.86,0:06:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once breakfast is over,\Nshow her around the base.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.05,0:06:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.86,0:06:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'm really busy,\Nbut it was an order,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm showing you around\Nbecause I have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.26,0:06:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right. Thank you, Kureha-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.66,0:06:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so informal, Private Sorami!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.91,0:06:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Private Suminoya-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.41,0:06:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:07:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then first, face the platoon and national flags...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.43,0:07:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Salute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 1121 Platoon presently\Nconsists of five members:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.06,0:07:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lieutenant, a sergeant, a corporal,\Nand two privates. Five in total.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.23,0:07:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Private Suminoya-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the absolute minimum\Nrequired for a platoon. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.40,0:07:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means we're all elites.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our platoon has been given\Nthe following armaments:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.75,0:07:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One tank,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,one heavy machine gun,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.96,0:07:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,two light machine guns,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.79,0:07:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,four rifles,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,five handguns.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using these, our mission is to defend the\Nnational border around Seize, Trois.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.72,0:07:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.78,0:07:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Private Suminoya-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.90,0:07:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a question!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.52,0:08:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.65,0:08:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Permission to speak granted, Private Sorami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If, uh... If my memory is correct,\Nbeyond Seize is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.29,0:08:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct. Beyond the mountains\Nis a no man's land.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.48,0:08:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the borders of Helvetia only extend this far,\Nso this is a national border!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The front lines!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An important base!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we always keep watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.68,0:08:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The five of us,\Nthroughout the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.95,0:08:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sleeping during watch is\Nabsolutely forbidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.67,0:08:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only hotline in the city\Nthat's connected to the Capitol.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.97,0:08:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.51,0:08:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it rings, something big\Nis about to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.77,0:08:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it does, everyone's woken up\Nand put on alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Private Suminoya-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second floor contains the captain's\Nquarters and the briefing room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Under normal circumstances, entry is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.38,0:09:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's perfectly all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.34,0:09:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But make sure you knock first!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the latrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.07,0:09:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bath drawing and cleaning duties\Nare assigned by rotation. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bathing is done in order\Nof rank, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.59,0:09:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more fun if we all\Nbathe together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.54,0:09:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.12,0:09:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cleaning the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.40,0:09:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's Noël's turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she seemed so tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.35,0:09:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll set a bad example\Nfor the rookie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.99,0:09:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just go sit somewhere and\Nact captain-ish for a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.23,0:10:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, take a good look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.51,0:10:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the 1121st's\Nmain battle tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vector-Type Zero Autonomous\NTank Walker, the Takemikazuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.66,0:10:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's much bigger than the one\Nat the training grounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.80,0:10:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is one of the so-called\Nzero-generation tanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a relic from the past.\NThere are fewer than ten left in the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard of them.\NThey're supposed to be really amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.52,0:10:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But its legs...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.64,0:10:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's undergoing repair.\NThere aren't enough parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:11:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-OK, so there's no manual either,\Nand we can't even find most of the parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Noël will take care\Nof it somehow, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare call it useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure someday it will...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make fun of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.32,0:11:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know we're lax.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.18,0:11:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're lax as heck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.07,0:11:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They call us the useless Seize squad\Nor say we're just for decoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.83,0:11:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're a pink squad,\Nyet we don't even have a working tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it for your tour!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.81,0:11:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.54,0:11:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like they're getting along.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.94,0:11:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.42,0:11:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like we did, when we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.83,0:11:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.95,0:11:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's a bit of a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.54,0:12:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After I sent you after Kana-chan last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, why is she communications?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.34,0:12:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said the new recruit was going\Nto be a loader or a pilot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.01,0:12:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not up to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Command sent her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.64,0:12:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the army, you don't always\Nget what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.26,0:12:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, there. It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio will take care of you, too,\Njust as she always has.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.34,0:12:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And of course, so will I.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.05,0:12:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's got pretty good intuition,\Nso she may have realized something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.61,0:12:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.25,0:12:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saw what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.07,0:13:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.91,0:13:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.22,0:13:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.73,0:13:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were just tired\Nand seeing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.79,0:13:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean,\Nyou thought so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.47,0:13:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.95,0:13:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was in the barracks, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.09,0:13:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.59,0:13:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't encourage her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.82,0:13:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's nothing special\Nabout ghosts, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.19,0:13:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you, too, Noël!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.59,0:13:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an engineer.\NGo investigate like one and then report back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.81,0:13:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.63,0:13:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.45,0:13:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no ghosts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't! There aren't!\NThere aren't! There aren't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.03,0:14:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. There are no ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.45,0:14:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.21,0:14:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.59,0:14:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.36,0:14:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give the place a thorough investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.44,0:14:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blow your trumpet if you\Nencounter the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.32,0:14:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll send reinforcements!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.37,0:14:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.10,0:14:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Private-dono...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Kana... Private!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is kinda fun, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lightning sounds like\Na marching beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.85,0:14:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.03,0:14:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.68,0:14:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Kana... Private Sorami!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.46,0:14:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're on point.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll back you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.85,0:14:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.47,0:15:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place has stayed the way\Nit was before it was a fort.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it before?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How am I supposed to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.04,0:15:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.59,0:15:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.24,0:15:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ideographs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.65,0:15:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.09,0:15:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't read it, so put it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.68,0:15:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be wonderful\Nif I could read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably some\Njunk from long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.29,0:16:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.72,0:16:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.13,0:16:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But ghosts protect us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.59,0:16:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.71,0:16:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the village where I was born, we had an annual\Nfestival to celebrate and thank the ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.81,0:16:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where in the middle of nowhere\Nwere you born?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, ghosts possess people, drink their blood,\Nmove corpses, and lots of nasty stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.47,0:16:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.62,0:16:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes rats carry\Nbad diseases...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.99,0:16:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.15,0:16:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you are scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.14,0:17:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.66,0:17:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.27,0:17:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.68,0:17:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Private-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.03,0:17:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking...\NMaybe this was a school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.31,0:17:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.85,0:17:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no school this size,\Neven in the Capitol.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.76,0:17:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there used to be a lot\Nmore people, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm sure, in this school,\Nthere were a bunch of kids our age.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.44,0:17:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They all studied together...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.62,0:17:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they taught music here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.12,0:17:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outside the army?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:17:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.99,0:18:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.53,0:18:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't read the words, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.49,0:18:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sounds don't change...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.48,0:18:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you standing there for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.25,0:18:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kureha-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's wonderful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.17,0:18:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.05,0:18:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.08,0:18:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The town of Seize, this building,\Neveryone in our platoon... They're all...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.58,0:19:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just a useless troop\Nin the middle of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.29,0:19:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our tank doesn't work,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.62,0:19:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they forget to supply\Nus a lot of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We never get any real missions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.28,0:19:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all so lax...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.97,0:19:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you love it, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.63,0:19:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.68,0:19:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.76,0:19:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.24,0:19:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.49,0:19:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.38,0:19:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the gunner of the 1121st,\Nand it's a wonderful place,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.47,0:19:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I love it more than anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's our ghost, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you mistake\Nthis for a ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.41,0:20:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.66,0:20:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look a lot like that\Nthief from yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.69,0:20:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you... You're tonight's dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.63,0:20:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't frighten her\Nwhen she's hurt, Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.51,0:20:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she has no place else to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.80,0:20:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what's our symbol?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.90,0:20:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't be right to cook her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.95,0:20:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Shuko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.91,0:20:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She {\i1}named{\i0} it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.36,0:20:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think it's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.65,0:20:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, you almost died,\Nthanks to this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.42,0:20:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But today, thanks to it, I was able\Nto have a great adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.43,0:20:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Kureha-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.48,0:21:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.49,0:21:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't even classify that\Nas a {\i1}little{\i0} adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh. I guess majority rule wins here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.69,0:21:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.13,0:21:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.91,0:21:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But next time you steal food,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll be punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.24,0:22:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was Rio this morning, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.10,0:22:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd start getting complaints from the\Ntown if Kanata did it every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.37,0:22:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.76,0:22:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's your seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.77,0:22:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.60,0:22:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just happened to find\Nanother seat like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.55,0:22:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do it special for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.41,0:22:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.49,0:22:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.38,0:22:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.48,0:22:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.15,0:22:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.35,0:22:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.70,0:22:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Breakfast...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.97,0:24:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}A Day with the Squad - Rio Runs
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.68,0:24:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.89,0:24:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Day with the Squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.13,0:24:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio Runs.
